to say with some <HI>Alteration</HI> of the <HI>Question</HI> put to <HI>Esther,</HI> viz. <HI>Who
knoweth not that he is come to</HI> Rome'<HI>s</HI> See <HI>for such a time as this is?</HI></P>
<P>The <HI>Mountainous</HI> heap of <HI>Rubbish</HI> in the <HI>Iesuites</HI> and other <HI>Casuists Prin|ciples</HI>
(and even in the <HI>Canon</HI> Law) appears very stupendious to the World,
