<P>But in <HI>Answer</HI> to which I shall do that right to the <HI>Papacy</HI> to clear the
<HI>mistake</HI> in the <HI>objection,</HI> and inform the <HI>Reader</HI> that tho <HI>Alexander</HI> the 7th
did <HI>Ex Cathedra,</HI> damn that <HI>Sorbon</HI>-Censure as aforesaid, yet it appears
