and others of that Nature, however so much <HI>disgusted</HI> by the <HI>bulk</HI> of the
Nation, such <HI>bulky</HI> and voluminous <HI>Controversial</HI> writing of them, as was
long ago in use, is nauseous to the age, and the time spent in reading Mat|ters
