faln <HI>mad</HI> for <HI>love</HI> of him.</P>
<P>One part of your Power, namely that wherein you are a Conduit-Pipe to
convey the grants of Honour and profit from your <HI>Royal Master,</HI> the <HI>Foun|tain</HI>
of Honour, 'tis possible for you to quit, and that with pleasure too, that
