<P>And the truth is, it is already through the Providence Divine, and like|wise
the Providence and Circumspection of Men so effected, That these
<HI>lewd Moralists,</HI> that call themselves the <HI>Fellows</HI> of the <HI>Holy Iesus,</HI> these
<HI>crafty Companions</HI> are so detected in the Church, not only as <HI>Cheats,</HI> but as
