<HI>Comedy,</HI> a sort of military <HI>pretenders,</HI> who after their Buffetings and Spurn<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">ings
they had took from so many, did support their Credit only by this <HI>Com|bined</HI>
Determination, namely, <HI>that they were valiant among themselves:</HI> and
