<HI>Book</HI> 7th, <HI>that</HI> Laymez <HI>the</HI> General <HI>of the</HI> Iesuites spoke with great veh<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">men<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters">
and Master-like in the Councel about two hours, proving that the Power of Iu|risdiction
