none might think it to be necessary, and thought it sufficient to say <HI>pr<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">sente Con|cilio?</HI>
How comes the Case now alter'd, when we behold the Iesuites now cruci|fying
