Translated into <HI>English,</HI> and call'd, <HI>The Policy of the Clergy of</HI> France <HI>to de|stroy
the Protestants of that Kingdom,</HI> and writ in the way of a Dialogue be|tween
a <HI>Parisian</HI> and <HI>Provincial,</HI> where <HI>p.</HI> 67, and 68. <HI>Le Cheise</HI> and the Ie|suits
