<HI>of the</HI> Faith, <HI>I will without any tergiversation or excuse execute, as far as I
am able (for this is the Jesuits fourth Vow to the Pope) shall I then be active
in the</HI> hindring a Decree of this Nature, <HI>given by this Judge from being exe|cuted,
at the</HI> same time, I Protest against it, shall I make no Protestation
