<P>For the determining the truth about such Principles, he need not say as
one of his <HI>Predecessors</HI> did about the <HI>Iansenian Speculations, that he had no skill
in Divinity.</HI> A very little skill in <HI>Natural Divinity</HI> (and such as may be had
