to the <HI>advantage</HI> of <HI>Popery</HI> or <HI>Enthusiasme,</HI> I hope your Lordship will acquit
me both of <HI>Singularity</HI> and <HI>Enthusiasme</HI> as to the <HI>opinion</HI> I have given, espe|cially
since I only profess it to be founded on Natural Reason, and do only
