<PB N="71" REF="87">
thus <HI>Buchanan</HI> in his <HI>Scotch History</HI> saith that in <HI>H.</HI> the 8<HI>ths</HI> time, <HI><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">antaque
erat caecitas ut sacerdotum plerique novitatis nomine offensi, eum librum a Marti|no</HI>
Luthero <HI>nuper fuisse Scriptum affirmarent ac vetus testamentum reposcerent&punc;
