<P><HI>Harry</HI> the 8<HI>th</HI> therefore did in his Contest with the Papacy <HI>Ferire faciem,</HI>
and <HI>did fight neither against small and great but the King of Rome,</HI> as I may say.
He attaqued the Pope in his claim of authority over all Christians, the autho|rity
