<P>I account therefore in <HI>Harry</HI> the 8<HI>ths</HI> time Poperies most <HI>sensible</HI> and <HI>vital</HI>
part, viz. the <HI>Popes supremacy</HI> did end in <HI>England per simplicem desinentiam.</HI>
