dispensationum, similium&abque; fraudum immens&acirc; copi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> infinitis pecuniis</HI>
Anglos <HI>emunxerunt.</HI></P>
<P>Nothing less then <HI>infinity</HI> of Treasure out of one Island could supply the
