some Critical <HI>Calculators</HI>) the whole Laity would be <HI>nichil'd,</HI> as the <HI>Exche|quer</HI>
word is.</P>
<P>King <HI>Edward</HI> the First, as the <HI>Antiq. Britan.</HI> mention, sent some of his
