it self, and to make the <HI>sacredness</HI> of all <HI>Oaths</HI> whatsoever to evapo|rate.</P>
<P><PB N="292" REF="201">
Let any <HI>sober</HI> Person of the <HI>Dissenters</HI> Party but seriously read that
