Descent.</P>
<P>The <HI>Promise</HI> in the <HI>Clause</HI> of the <HI>Oath</HI> of <HI>Supremacy</HI> runneth thus, <HI>viz.</HI>
and <HI>DO Promise</HI> that FROM HENCEFORTH I WILL <HI>bear
Faith,</HI> &amp;c. And words could not express an actual Obligation incurr'd
