Throne of God,</HI> and the <HI>Style</HI> of Crown'd Heads is <HI>Dei grati&acirc;,</HI> and <HI>by him
Kings Reign.</HI></P>
<P>But to proceed. If there could be <HI>Ambiguity</HI> in the word <HI>Heirs,</HI> the
