&amp; libertates suas illaesas,</HI> and whereby the <HI>British</HI> Churches are secu|red
under a Prince of any Religion from <HI>Foreign</HI> Arbitrary impositions
But indeed the Style current in <HI>Magna Charta</HI> is, that our <HI>Kings</HI> for
<HI>themselves and their Heirs</HI> forever, did grant the Customs and Liberties
