FROM THIS DAY FORWARDS I will be Faithful and Loyal
to our Lord the King AND HIS HEIRS,</HI> &amp;c.</P>
<P><PB N="295" REF="202">
<HI>The instances are innumerable of Allegiance anciently Sworn to our</HI>
Kings <HI>and their</HI> Heirs; <HI>and this one for example occureth to me as
