<P>And tho the <HI>Statute</HI> of 1^<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">. <HI>Elizabethae,</HI> in the <HI>Clause</HI> of the Annex|ing
Ecclesiastical Jurisdiction to the Crown, useth the <HI>style</HI> of <HI>Your High|ness,
