full Power,</HI> &amp;c. as the <HI>Statue</HI> of the Supremacy 26^o. <HI>Henry 8th.</HI>
runs in the <HI>Style</HI> of <HI>our Sovereign Lord, his Heirs and Successors, Kings
of this Realms, shall be taken, accepted, and reputed, the only Supreme
Head,</HI> and tho the <HI>Oath</HI> in the 35<HI>th. H.</HI> the 8<HI>th. Cap.</HI> 1. that re|lates
to <HI>the bearing Faith, Truth, and true Allegiance to the Kings Maje|sty,
and to his Heirs and Successors,</HI> &amp;c. be further thus expressed, <HI>viz.
