the great Privilege that Christianity hath ennobled Humane Nature with in
being</HI> Heirs of God and joynt Heirs with Christ <HI>as St.</HI> Pauls <HI>words are,
and of being</HI> Heirs according to the Promise; <HI>and may all the Divine</HI> Pro|mises
be <HI>so</HI> Yea and Amen <HI>to me, and interpreted with not only a plain but a
