<P>And by Virtue of the <HI>Moral</HI> Offices of <HI>honouring all men,</HI> and of the
<HI>Internal</HI> Communion <HI>due from all Christians to all Christians,</HI> I shall with|out
offending the <HI>Church</HI> I hold <HI>External</HI> Communion with, venture to
