<HI>Angels Cul<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="2 letters"> latriae,</HI> and on such as in the <HI>Eucharist</HI> determine the
thoughts of their worship to the <HI>Consecrated</HI> Bread. But I believe there
