Law (for he saith there, That <HI>that Law tho not appertaining to Christi|stians,
Sub ratione legis sperialiter obligantis,</HI> yet is so <HI>sub ratione doctrinae,
quatenus vel generali su&acirc; natur&acirc; vel proportionis aequit<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">te exhibet sempe<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter"> no|bis
