quisquam mortalium id Iuris sibi arr<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="tech" EXTENT="1 letter">gare ut qui Dei in terris Mini|ster
&amp; Vice-Deus futurus sit, omnem illam suam authoritatem &amp; potestatem
ab ipso sibi collatam agnoscat?</HI></P>
<P>Let all such then who did <HI>AVDERE</HI> thus in the Affair of our <HI>Here|ditary</HI>
